pi-camera-control (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Intervalometer and remote control for Canon CCAPI cameras
  * Web-based interface for camera control
  * Dual WiFi mode support (Access Point + Client)
  * Real-time camera status monitoring
  * Battery and thermal monitoring
  * Automatic network configuration for Raspberry Pi
  * Systemd service for reliable operation
  * Optimized for astrophotography and timelapse

